{"id":8209,"date":"2026-02-03T10:17:29","date_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:17:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8209"},"modified":"2026-02-03T10:17:29","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:17:29","slug":"centella-asiatica-extract-lam-diu-phuc-hoi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/centella-asiatica-extract-lam-diu-phuc-hoi\/","title":{"rendered":"Centella Asiatica Extract \u2013 L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u1ec7u quen thu\u1ed9c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Centella Asiatica (Rau M\u00e1) b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m v\u1edbi \u201cb\u1ed9 t\u1ee9\u201d tr\u1ee9 danh: asiaticoside, madecassoside, asiatic acid, madecassic acid. D\u1eef li\u1ec7u hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu \u2013 ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 \u2013 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 li\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o khi d\u00f9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-centella-asiatica-extract\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Centella Asiatica Extract<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc &amp; c\u00e1ch g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1c: <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Centella asiatica<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (rau m\u00e1, gotu kola). Trong INCI th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p: Centella Asiatica Extract, Madecassoside, Asiaticoside, Asiatic Acid, Madecassic Acid. L\u00e0 nh\u00f3m triterpenoid saponin v\u00e0 triterpenic acids c\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh sinh h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c khoa h\u1ecdc \u2013 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng: Rau m\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi trong y h\u1ecdc truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng (ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9). Khi tinh s\u1ea1ch ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n h\u00f3a chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t, Centella tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da sau treatment, v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8211\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8211\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8211 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-2.webp\" alt=\"Centella Asiatica \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8211\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Centella Asiatica \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Centella Asiatica Extract r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0 a chu\u1ed9ng \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m H\u00e0n v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng Madecassoside v\u00e0 Asiaticoside \u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-centella-asiatica-extract\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Centella Asiatica Extract<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu &amp; gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf: L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu c\u00e1c ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam, cho c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu khi da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng nh\u1eb9, \u0111\u1ecf do m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng hay actives m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 li\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f4ng: th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u0103ng sinh nguy\u00ean b\u00e0o s\u1ee3i v\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p collagen giai \u0111o\u1ea1n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa m\u00f4; h\u1eefu \u00edch sau peel nh\u1eb9, laser vi \u0111i\u1ec3m (theo ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o: c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n TEWL (m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc qua bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec) khi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u, b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t m\u1ecbn, \u1ea9m h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1: qu\u00e9t g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o do UV (kh\u00f4ng thay th\u1ebf kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch do actives: th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y khi routine c\u00f3 retinoid, AHA\/BHA, benzoyl peroxide, Centella \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 gi\u00fap da \u00edt bong tr\u00f3c ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Triterpenoid saponin &amp; acids (asiaticoside\/madecassoside\/asiatic acid\/madecassic acid) \u0111i\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn vi\u00eam (NF-\u03baB, cytokine), k\u00edch th\u00edch ECM (collagen type I\/III) v\u00e0 t\u0103ng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n protein h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o (filaggrin, involucrin theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u).<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y trung h\u00f2a c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do (ROS), gi\u1ea3m stress oxy h\u00f3a v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 c\u00e1c mao m\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u1edbi da, nh\u1edd v\u1eady hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1eedng \u0111\u1ecf tho\u00e1ng qua d\u1ecbu l\u1ea1i nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Toner\/essence\/ampoule: chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t to\u00e0n ph\u1ea7n 0,2\u20132% ho\u1eb7c \u201cCica complex\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Serum\/kem ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i: madecassoside\/asiaticoside tinh s\u1ea1ch (0,05\u20130,3%) ph\u1ed1i panthenol, ceramide.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gel\/cream l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu sau treatment: n\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u, \u00edt c\u1ed3n; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u00eam allantoin, HA.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m ch\u1ea5t n\u1ec1n: Hi\u1ec7n nay m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i g\u1ed1c n\u01b0\u1edbc trong c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh tinh ch\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1 gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh cho s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8212\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8212\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8212 size-full\" style=\"font-size: 16px\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-3.webp\" alt=\"\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng Centella Asiatica Extract l\u00e0m ch\u1ea5t n\u1ec1n\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8212\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng Centella Asiatica Extract l\u00e0m ch\u1ea5t n\u1ec1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-duong-sang-ngay-mela-gsc\/?_gl=1*csiws0*_up*MQ..&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQiA1czLBhDhARIsAIEc7uhO20WtzLakS_BBYCast0rmxiHqa0_G_IY5AbaiTgJ6lP7j5yJxaRoaAniDEALw_wcB&amp;gbraid=0AAAAA_YZ5LfGYb4T6bYbYh5BZsM_4myxG\">Serum \u201ckh\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d Mela GSC<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-centella-asiatica-extract-sao-cho-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Centella Asiatica Extract sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung-centella-asiatica-extract\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Centella Asiatica Extract<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, \u0111ang k\u00edch \u1ee9ng nh\u1eb9, \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t do kh\u00f4, ng\u1ed3i trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0 l\u00e2u, da b\u1ecfng r\u00e1t do ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau treatment nh\u1eb9 (AHA\/BHA n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p, retinoid m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen, waxing\/c\u1ea1o r\u00e2u, peel nh\u1eb9, laser vi \u0111i\u1ec3m theo ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ee5n \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb (retinoid\/BPO\/kh\u00e1ng sinh b\u00f4i): c\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p \u2013 thi\u00ean kh\u00f4 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o, gi\u1eef \u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh-centella-asiatica-extract\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh Centella Asiatica Extract<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ednh an to\u00e0n t\u1ed1t: hi\u1ebfm khi g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng; tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m n\u00ean xem k\u1ef9 nh\u00e3n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n. Tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed3n v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb nguy\u00ean th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt: ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 vi\u00eam da ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt n\u00ean patch test 24\u201348h (sau tai\/vi\u1ec1n h\u00e0m) tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng di\u1ec7n r\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da \u0111ang vi\u00eam c\u1ea5p\/vi\u00eam da c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba: tham kh\u1ea3o b\u00e1c s\u0129\u2014Centella h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng thay th\u1ebf thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8213\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8213\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8213 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-4.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Rau-ma-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8213\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh ch\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3. D\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da Centella\/ madecassoside \u1edf n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem an to\u00e0n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong kem ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u. V\u1eabn n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecdc k\u1ef9 nh\u00e3n, tr\u00e1nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a tinh d\u1ea7u th\u01a1m m\u1ea1nh; khi c\u00f3 b\u1ec7nh da li\u1ec5u n\u1ec1n, tham kh\u1ea3o b\u00e1c s\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n tham kh\u1ea3o:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ingredients derived from the Herb Centella asiatica. (n.d.). Cosmetics Info. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cosmeticsinfo.org\/ingredient\/ingredients-derived-from-the-herb-centella-asiatica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.cosmeticsinfo.org\/ingredient\/ingredients-derived-from-the-herb-centella-asiatica\/<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u200c<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Centella Asiatica Extract (chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1) \u2013 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf \u2013 l\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8210,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8209","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8209","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8209"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8209\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8921,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8209\/revisions\/8921"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8210"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8209"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8209"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=8209"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}